tablish and create a new department of Biobank in our institution&quot;\",\"link\":\"http:\\/\\/eb3kitlearning\\/2018\\/01\\/29\\/dr-zivile-gudleviciene-national-cancer-institute-lithuania-500\\/\",\"text2\":\"undefined\",\"image_url\":\"http:\\/\\/eb3kitlearning\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/01\\/Lith-1-300x255.png\",\"title\":\"Dr Zivile Gudleviciene\",\"subtitle\":\"National Cancer Institute, Lithuania\",\"social_repeater\":\"undefined\",\"id\":\"customizer_repeater_56d7ea7f40d56\",\"shortcode\":\"undefined\"},{\"text\":\"&quot;Always the best aspect is to meet other people and share your ideas and experiences and find out that we are still on the same level despite the fact that we are from different parts of the world&quot;\",\"link\":\"http:\\/\\/eb3kitlearning\\/2018\\/01\\/29\\/dr-lukasz-kozera-wroclaw-researchh-centre-eit-116\\/\",\"text2\":\"undefined\",\"image_url\":\"http:\\/\\/eb3kitlearning\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/01\\/Pola-2-300x265.png\",\"title\":\"Dr Lukasz Kosera\",\"subtitle\":\"Wroclaw Research Centre EIT+, Poland\",\"social_repeater\":\"undefined\",\"id\":\"customizer_repeater_56d7ea7f40d66\",\"shortcode\":\"undefined\"},{\"text\":\"&quot;I got to learn so many things, especially with the data, because I knew some few basics then during the training I got to learn way more&quot;\",\"link\":\"http:\\/\\/eb3kitlearning\\/2018\\/01\\/29\\/ms-deborah-boateng-peace-and-love-hospital-340\\/\",\"text2\":\"undefined\",\"image_url\":\"http:\\/\\/eb3kitlearning\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/01\\/Ghan-1-300x232.png\",\"title\":\"Ms Deborah Boateng\",\"subtitle\":\"Peace and Love Hospital, Ghana\",\"social_repeater\":\"undefined\",\"id\":\"customizer_repeater_56d7ea7f40d76\",\"shortcode\":\"undefined\"}]\";s:19:\"hestia_team_content\";s:2067:\"[{\"icon_value\":\"fa-twitter\",\"text\":\"B3Africa aims to implement a cooperation framework and technical informatics platform for biobank integration between Africa and Europe. The informatics platform includes a set of open-source informatics tools for biobank and research activities.\",\"link\":\"http:\\/\\/www.b3Africa.org\",\"text2\":\"undefined\",\"image_url\":\"http:\\/\\/eb3kitlearning\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2017\\/10\\/logoB3Africa-baseline-web-transparent_300x300-1.png\",\"title\":\"Bridging Biobanking and Biomedical Research Across Europe and Africa\",\"subtitle\":\"B3Africa\",\"social_repeater\":\"[{&quot;icon&quot;:&quot;fa-twitter&quot;,&quot;link&quot;:&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;twitter.com&#x2F;hashtag&#x2F;B3Africa?src=hash&quot;,&quot;id&quot;:&quot;customizer-repeater-social-repeater-57fb908674e06&quot;},{&quot;icon&quot;:&quot;fa-info-circle&quot;,&quot;link&quot;:&quot;www.b3Africa.org&quot;,&quot;id&quot;:&quot;customizer-repeater-social-repeater-5a69c74718137&quot;}]\",\"id\":\"customizer_repeater_56d7ea7f40c56\",\"shortcode\":\"undefined\"},{\"icon_value\":\"fa-twitter\",\"text\":\"The Biobank and Cohort building Network (BCNet) was established by IARC in 2013 as an opportunity for LMIC members and international partners to jointly address existing challenges in biobanking infrastructure, including ethical, legal and social issues (ELSIs).\",\"link\":\"http:\\/\\/bcnet.iarc.fr\\/\",\"text2\":\"undefined\",\"image_url\":\"http:\\/\\/eb3kitlearning\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/02\\/Artboard-1.png\",\"title\":\"Low-and Middle-Income Countries (LMIC) Biobank and Cohort Building Network\",\"subtitle\":\"BCNet\",\"social_repeater\":\"[{&quot;icon&quot;:&quot;fa-twitter&quot;,&quot;link&quot;:&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;twitter.com&#x2F;hashtag&#x2F;BCNetLMIC?src=hash&quot;,&quot;id&quot;:&quot;customizer-repeater-social-repeater-57fb9155a1072&quot;},{&quot;icon&quot;:&quot;fa-info-circle&quot;,&quot;link&quot;:&quot;http:&#x2F;&#x2F;bcnet.iarc.fr&#x2F;&quot;,&quot;id&quot;:&quot;customizer-repeater-social-repeater-57fb9160ab683&quot;}]\",\"id\":\"customizer_repeater_56d7ea7f40c66\",\"shortcode\":\"undefined\"}]\";s:18:\"hestia_page_editor\";s:741:\"<h2 style=\"text-align: center\">Recognizing the <span style=\"color: #d96b0c\">diversity</span> <span style=\"color: #d96b0c\">of professionals</span> working up-and down-stream of biobanking</h2><p style=\"text-align: center\">The design and implementation of this portal is based on comprehensive situational analysis and learning needs assessment conducted in the frame of the BCNet initiative and B3Africa project.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">It reflects the growing needs for multidisciplinary teams to address contemporary challenges in biobank-based research.</p><p></p><p><img src=\"http://eb3kitlearning/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/personas-300x87.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"87\" class=\"aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1110\" /></p>\";s:21:\"hestia_portfolio_hide\";b:0;s:18:\"hestia_ribbon_hide\";b:1;s:26:\"hestia_contact_content_new\";s:47:\"<div class=\"info info-horizontal\">Testing</div>\";s:27:\"hestia_big_title_background\";s:70:\"http://eb3kitlearning/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/PF2C9565_1325-548.jpg\";s:21:\"hestia_big_title_text\";s:55:\"Training professionals up-and down-stream of biobanking\";s:13:\"show_on_front\";s:4:\"page\";s:22:\"hestia_big_title_title\";s:16:\"Biobank Learning\";s:26:\"hestia_page_sidebar_layout\";s:12:\"sidebar-left\";s:27:\"hestia_enable_scroll_to_top\";b:1;s:24:\"hestia_feature_thumbnail\";s:129:\"http://eb3kitlearning/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/18.2-contributing-to-better-infrastructure-for-medical-research_compressed-1.jpg\";s:26:\"hestia_clients_bar_content\";s:1721:\"[{\"text\":\"undefined\",\"link\":\"#\",\"text2\":\"undefined\",\"image_url\":\"http:\\/\\/biobanklearning.iarc.fr\\/wp-content\\/plugins\\/themeisle-companion\\/obfx_modules\\/companion-legacy\\/inc\\/hestia\\/inc\\/img\\/clients1.png\",\"title\":\"undefined\",\"subtitle\":\"undefined\",\"social_repeater\":\"undefined\",\"id\":\"social-repeater-5a698ff8d60a7\",\"shortcode\":\"undefined\"},{\"text\":\"undefined\",\"link\":\"#\",\"text2\":\"unde